init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens want to know what it is that humans find so special about Damon, and why their interest in him is so great.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: The aliens want to know what it is that humans find so special about Damon, and why their interest in him is so great.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Wee want to trade him for a female of our kind," he concluded.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Apparently satisfied the deal was a good one, it grunted then opened a cage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A green female with an eyestalk the size of her body emerged from the cage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien gestured to the female, then to the bundle behind Svirrak.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Your female isss a little skinny," the alien noted, rubbing its chin again.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: Your female isss a little skinny,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Svirrak took the human off his back, then dropped it into the cage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm an Oscar winning actor in the film 'Good Will Hunting'.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're an alien with a freaking hammer on its head!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You don't want to mess with me!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt said, pointing at the hammerhead.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien just stared at him as he was dropped into the cage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien then closed the cage door and locked it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: said the hammerhead with a grin on its face.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We'll see how you react when we take you to the..."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien stopped in mid-sentence when it was suddenly hit by an arrow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The hammerhead fell to the ground.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Svirrak and the female alien looked at each other, then sighed as they raised their hands.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As soon as the hammerhead aliens saw that the Airforce soldiers had arrived, they all raised their hands.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Airforce officers quickly rounded up the aliens and handcuffed them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon stepped out of the cage and dusted himself off.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "My arm's a little sore, but I think I'm fine," he said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We'll take you to the safety of Area 51.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: From there we'll get a helicopter to take you home.
